title: Shot in the Dark
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Open 24/7 coffee shop environment. Menu is heavy on meat, dairy, and egg but does offer soy drink options (at extra charge), ovo-lacto breakfast all day, a veggie wrap, a veggie burger (with vegan pattie made in-house) - vegans can ask to hold the mayonnaise, and vegan cookies. Has Wi-Fi.
